      "name": "ASTM F1717 static compression-bending operating envelope — non-cannulated 7.5 mm construct",
      "description": "Axial compressive load range: 0–2500 N applied at 10 mm/min crosshead displacement rate (ASTM F1717 §8.3). Screw outer diameter: 7.5 mm ± 0.05 mm. Rod diameter: 5.5 mm ± 0.05 mm. Construct span (pedicle screw tip to rod end): 60–65 mm. Test temperature: 23 ± 2 °C in ambient air. Displacement range evaluated: 0–40 mm. Boundary points explicitly covered by the N=11 bench constructs across two laboratories (Lab A: 0–1800 N; Lab B: 0–2500 N), confirming model validity at both ends of the declared envelope."
    },
    "hasApplicabilityConstraint": {
